      • updateElement

        public void updateElement(WebSocketChannelDTO channel)
        Notifies all EventListenerList that the state of the connection of the given WebSocketChannelDTO channel has been changed. If the given channel is not present in this ComboBoxChannelModel no action is taken.

        Should be called when the state of the connection of the given channel changes to WebSocketProxy.State.CLOSED.

        Implementation Note: Only the field WebSocketChannelDTO.endTimestamp is updated because it's the only field that is used to tell how the connection state is displayed.

        Parameters:
        channel - the channel that has changed.
